{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"Hello, everyone. Because this is my first time at TED,"},{"time":6000,"text":"I've decided to bring along an old friend"},{"time":8000,"text":"to help break the ice a bit."},{"time":12000,"text":"Yes. That's right. This is Barbie."},{"time":15000,"text":"She's 50 years old. And she's looking as young as ever."},{"time":18000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":19000,"text":"But I'd also like to introduce you to"},{"time":21000,"text":"what may be an unfamiliar face."},{"time":25000,"text":"This is Fulla. Fulla is the Arab world's answer to Barbie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"Now, according to proponents of the clash of civilizations,"},{"time":33000,"text":"Barbie and Fulla occupy these completely separate spheres."},{"time":37000,"text":"They have different interests. They have divergent values."},{"time":40000,"text":"And should they ever come in contact ..."},{"time":43000,"text":"well, I've got to tell you, it's just not going to be pretty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"My experience, however, in the Islamic world is very different."},{"time":50000,"text":"Where I work, in the Arab region,"},{"time":52000,"text":"people are busy taking up Western innovations"},{"time":54000,"text":"and changing them into things"},{"time":56000,"text":"which are neither conventionally Western,"},{"time":58000,"text":"nor are they traditionally Islamic."},{"time":60000,"text":"I want to show you two examples."},{"time":62000,"text":"The first is 4Shbab."},{"time":64000,"text":"It means \"for youth\" and it's a new Arab TV channel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"(Video): Video clips from across the globe."},{"time":71000,"text":"The USA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73000,"text":"♫ I am not afraid to stand alone ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"♫ I am not afraid to stand alone, if Allah is by my side ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"♫ I am not afraid to stand alone ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"♫ Everything will be all right ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"♫ I am not afraid to stand alone ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"The Arab world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"♫ She was preserved by modesty of the religion ♫"},{"time":109000,"text":"♫ She was adorned by the light of the Quran ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"Shereen El Feki: 4Shbab has been dubbed Islamic MTV."},{"time":122000,"text":"Its creator, who is an Egyptian TV producer"},{"time":124000,"text":"called Ahmed Abu Haïba,"},{"time":126000,"text":"wants young people to be inspired"},{"time":128000,"text":"by Islam to lead better lives."},{"time":131000,"text":"He reckons the best way to get that message across"},{"time":133000,"text":"is to use the enormously popular medium of music videos."},{"time":137000,"text":"4Shbab was set up as an alternative"},{"time":140000,"text":"to existing Arab music channels."},{"time":142000,"text":"And they look something like this."},{"time":144000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"That, by the way is Haifa Wehbe. She's a Lebanese pop star"},{"time":155000,"text":"and pan-Arab pin-up girl."},{"time":158000,"text":"In the world of 4Shbab, it's not about bump and grind."},{"time":161000,"text":"But it's not about fire and brimstone either."},{"time":164000,"text":"Its videos are intended to show"},{"time":166000,"text":"a kinder, gentler face of Islam,"},{"time":169000,"text":"for young people to deal with life's challenges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"Now, my second example is for a slightly younger crowd."},{"time":175000,"text":"And it's called \"The 99.\""},{"time":178000,"text":"Now, these are the world's first Islamic superheroes."},{"time":181000,"text":"They were created by a Kuwaiti psychologist"},{"time":183000,"text":"called Naif Al Mutawa."},{"time":185000,"text":"And his desire is to rescue Islam"},{"time":187000,"text":"from images of intolerance,"},{"time":189000,"text":"all in a child-friendly format."},{"time":193000,"text":"\"The 99.\" The characters are meant to embody"},{"time":195000,"text":"the 99 attributes of Allah:"},{"time":198000,"text":"justice, wisdom, mercy, among others."},{"time":201000,"text":"So, for example, there is the character of Noora."},{"time":205000,"text":"She is meant to have the power"},{"time":207000,"text":"to look inside people"},{"time":209000,"text":"and see the good and bad in everyone."},{"time":212000,"text":"Another character called Jami"},{"time":214000,"text":"has the ability to create fantastic inventions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"Now, \"The 99\" is not just a comic book."},{"time":220000,"text":"It's now a theme park."},{"time":222000,"text":"There is an animated series in the works."},{"time":224000,"text":"And by this time next year,"},{"time":226000,"text":"the likes of Superman and Wonder Woman"},{"time":228000,"text":"will have joined forces with \"The 99\""},{"time":230000,"text":"to beat injustice wherever they find it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"\"The 99\" and 4Shbab are just two of many examples"},{"time":239000,"text":"of this sort of Islamic cross-cultural hybridization."},{"time":243000,"text":"We're not talking here about a clash of civilizations."},{"time":246000,"text":"Nor is it some sort of indistinguishable mash."},{"time":249000,"text":"I like to think of it as a mesh of civilizations,"},{"time":252000,"text":"in which the strands of different cultures are intertwined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256000,"text":"Now, while 4Shbab and \"The 99\" may look new and shiny,"},{"time":259000,"text":"there is actually a very long tradition of this."},{"time":262000,"text":"Throughout its history, Islam has borrowed and adapted from other civilizations"},{"time":267000,"text":"both ancient and modern."},{"time":269000,"text":"After all, it's the Quran which encourages us to do this:"},{"time":274000,"text":"\"We made you into nations and tribes"},{"time":276000,"text":"so that you could learn from one another.\""},{"time":278000,"text":"And to my mind, those are pretty wise words,"},{"time":281000,"text":"no matter what your creed. Thank you."},{"time":284000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}